alcitabine with other drugs that have the potential to cause peripheral neuropathy should be avoided whenever possible.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/149046/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Sotorasib, Enasidenib, More', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Dolutegravir, More', 1767369485);
